{"word":"βαρέω","slug":"βαρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>βαρέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βαρύς\">βαρύς</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a>, only in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><i>depress, weigh down, burden</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of physical weariness affecting the eyes <b><a href='B:470 26:43'>Mt 26:43</a>; <a href='B:480 14:40'>Mk 14:40</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:490 9:32'>Lk 9:32</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of various other circumstances or conditions <b><a href='B:490 21:34'>Lk 21:34</a>; <a href='B:540 1:8'>2 Cor 1:8</a>; <a href='B:540 5:4'>5:4</a>; <a href='B:610 5:16'>1 Ti 5:16</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βάρβαρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:βαρέως\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}